        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the dish is hot, add the <strong>skinless chicken thighs</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
