    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is browning, top, tail and chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
