            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 10 min, remove the dish from the oven and stir through <strong>half </strong>your <strong>grated</strong> <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>macaroni </strong>with your <strong>shredded kale</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong>, then cover with a lid and return the dish to the oven for a further 15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once done, use two forks to shred the <strong>chicken</strong> apart and stir through your <strong>crème fraîche </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy chicken soup with macaroni</strong></p>",
