      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> creamy chicken soup with macaroni</strong> in a bowl, discard the <strong>bay</strong> <strong>leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and garnish with the <strong>crispy chicken skin</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
